      <title>大型科技公司呼吁对人工智能进行宽松的监管，但执法者却未能如愿</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/big-tech-s-call-for-light-touch-on-ai-falls-flat-with-enforcers</link>
